<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 06:17:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，欧盟将对中国电动汽车征收数十亿欧元的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-impose-multi-billion-euro-tariffs-chinese-evs-ft-reports-2024-06-12/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》援引知情人士消息称，欧盟委员会将于周三通知汽车制造商，从下个月起，将对进口中国电动汽车临时征收高达 25% 的额外关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 04:54:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-impose-multi-billion-euro-tariffs-chinese-evs-ft-reports-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>世界银行称缅甸贫困加剧，经济增长停滞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/myanmar-poverty-deepens-economic-growth-stagnant-world-bank-says-2024-06-12/</link><description>世界银行周三表示，缅甸的贫困现象比过去六年中任何时候都更加普遍，这个饱受冲突蹂躏的国家本财年的经济增长可能仍保持在区区 1%，而且几乎看不到任何喘息的迹象。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 04:38:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/myanmar-poverty-deepens-economic-growth-stagnant-world-bank-says-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>男子在通往台北的河流上被捕后，中国驳回了台湾的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-dismisses-taiwans-concerns-after-man-arrested-river-leading-taipei-2024-06-12/</link><description>中国政府周三表示，一名乘坐快艇穿越台湾海峡后在台北附近被捕的中国男子是单独行动，台湾不应如此可疑，这一案件引起了台湾安全官员的警惕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 03:35:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-dismisses-taiwans-concerns-after-man-arrested-river-leading-taipei-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>香港使用新的国家安全法来对付流亡活动人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-uses-new-national-security-law-against-exiled-activists-2024-06-12/</link><description>香港保安局周三表示，将动用新国家安全法中的权力来对付六名居住在英国的自我流亡活动人士，包括在他们逃离这座中国统治的城市后吊销他们的护照。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 03:17:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-uses-new-national-security-law-against-exiled-activists-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国通胀稳定，仍面临更多刺激措施的压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-inflation-rate-rises-steady-clip-factory-deflation-narrows-2024-06-12/</link><description>5月份，中国消费者通胀保持稳定，生产者价格跌幅有所放缓，但基本趋势表明，北京需要采取更多措施来支撑疲弱的内需和不平衡的经济复苏。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 02:06:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-inflation-rate-rises-steady-clip-factory-deflation-narrows-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>恒大电动汽车发出资产损失警告后股价下跌27%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/shares-evergrande-ev-unit-slide-27-after-it-warns-losing-assets-2024-06-12/</link><description>中国恒大新能源汽车集团表示面临失去土地和设备等关键资产的风险，周三该公司股价暴跌27%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 01:44:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/shares-evergrande-ev-unit-slide-27-after-it-warns-losing-assets-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>两名美国男子因串谋向中国出售伊朗石油而入狱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/two-us-men-jailed-conspiracy-sell-iranian-oil-china-2024-06-11/</link><description>美国司法部表示，两名得克萨斯州男子于 11 月被美国陪审团定罪，罪名是试图违反华盛顿实施的制裁，试图出售伊朗石油，并串谋洗钱，并于周二被判处 45 个月监禁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 23:18:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/two-us-men-jailed-conspiracy-sell-iranian-oil-china-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国特使警告匈牙利，与中国的密切关系“附带条件”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-envoy-warns-hungary-that-close-ties-with-china-come-with-strings-attached-2024-06-11/</link><description>美国驻布达佩斯特使周二严厉批评匈牙利政府与中国密切的政治和商业关系，这种关系往往“附带条件，而且往往以主权为代价”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 19:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-envoy-warns-hungary-that-close-ties-with-china-come-with-strings-attached-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>尽管韩国队失利，中国队仍保有世界杯预选赛的希望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/chinese-keep-world-cup-qualifying-hopes-alive-despite-korea-defeat-2024-06-11/</link><description>周二，中国队在首尔以0比1不敌韩国队，但仍以微弱优势晋级2026年世界杯亚洲区预选赛第三轮。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 15:52:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/chinese-keep-world-cup-qualifying-hopes-alive-despite-korea-defeat-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>荷兰情报机构称中国网络间谍活动范围超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/dutch-intelligence-says-chinese-cyber-espionage-goes-wider-than-it-suspected-2024-06-11/</link><description>荷兰军事情报部门周一表示，中国的网络间谍活动比其最初想象的更为广泛，其目标是西方政府和国防公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 15:43:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/dutch-intelligence-says-chinese-cyber-espionage-goes-wider-than-it-suspected-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国因维吾尔劳工而禁止从中国进口鞋类、海鲜、铝业公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/us-bars-imports-footwear-seafood-aluminum-firms-over-uyghur-labor-2024-06-11/</link><description>根据美国政府周二在网上发布的通知，美国又将三家公司列入禁止从涉嫌在中国强迫维吾尔人劳动的公司进口产品的名单。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 14:13:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/us-bars-imports-footwear-seafood-aluminum-firms-over-uyghur-labor-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>行业组织表示，尽管电动汽车关税调查，中国汽车制造商仍致力于欧洲市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automakers-committed-europe-despite-ev-tariff-probe-industry-group-says-2024-06-11/</link><description>中国一家领先的汽车工业协会周二表示，欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车进行反补贴调查不会影响中国汽车制造商在欧洲的投资计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 11:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automakers-committed-europe-despite-ev-tariff-probe-industry-group-says-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>随着西方制裁加剧，中国敦促金砖国家发挥更大作用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-greater-brics-role-western-sanctions-mount-2024-06-11/</link><description>外交部长王毅周二表示，在西方对中国实施制裁和贸易限制之后，中国敦促金砖国家集团承担更大责任，树立对世界的包容性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 10:50:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-greater-brics-role-western-sanctions-mount-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>越南总统希望妥善处理与中国的海上争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-president-wants-maritime-disputes-with-china-be-well-managed-2024-06-11/</link><description>越南国家主席苏林周二向中国驻河内大使熊波表示，妥善处理海事争端并尊重各国利益非常重要。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 09:17:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-president-wants-maritime-disputes-with-china-be-well-managed-2024-06-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国的折扣大战可能会巩固节俭的消费者心态</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-discount-wars-risk-cementing-frugal-consumer-mindset-2024-06-11/</link><description>中国低成本零售商积极抢占市场，为一些企业带来了丰厚的利润，但也加剧了激烈的价格战，加剧了世界第二大经济体的通货紧缩担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 07:37:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-discount-wars-risk-cementing-frugal-consumer-mindset-2024-06-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>